Package com.netflix.genie.common.internal.aws.s3

@ParametersAreNonnullByDefault package com.netflix.genie.common.internal.aws.s3
This package contains classes and utilities for working with the AWS S3 service.
Since:
4.0.0
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    BucketProperties
    A property class which holds information about how to interact with a specific S3 Bucket.
    S3ClientFactory
    An S3Client client factory class.
    S3ClientFactory.S3ClientKey
    A simple class used as a key to see if we already have a S3Client created for the combination of properties that make up this class.
    S3ProtocolResolver
    This class implements the ProtocolResolver interface.
    S3ProtocolResolverRegistrar
    A class which takes an instance of S3ProtocolResolver and adds it to the Spring ApplicationContext set of ProtocolResolver.
    S3TransferManagerFactory
    A factory class for creating and managing S3TransferManager instances.
    SimpleStorageRangeResource
    This class extends S3Resource in order to efficiently handle range requests.
